    "text": "whom I wished to keep with me, so that on your behalf he might minister to me in my imprisonment for the gospel;",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "PHP.1.7",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.3.1",
        "v": 4
      },
      {
        "r": "1CO.16.17",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "PHP.2.30",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "EPH.4.1",
        "v": 2
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.1",
        "v": 2
      }
    ],
    "section": null
  },
  "PHM.1.14": {
    "text": "but without your consent I did not want to do anything, so that your goodness would not be, in effect, by compulsion but of your own free will.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "2CO.9.7",
        "v": 8
      },
      {
        "r": "1PE.5.2-3",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "1CH.29.17",
        "v": 3
      },
      {
        "r": "PHM.1.8-9",
        "v": 2
