    "text": "For perhaps he was for this reason separated from you for a while, that you would have him back forever,",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "GEN.50.20",
        "v": 7
      },
      {
        "r": "GEN.45.5-8",
        "v": 4
