    "text": "At the same time also prepare me a lodging, for I hope that through your prayers I will be given to you.",
    "footnotes": [],
    "xrefs": [
      {
        "r": "2CO.1.11",
        "v": 5
      },
      {
        "r": "PHP.2.24",
